ion1 Value\": \"48\\\"\", \"Option2 Name\": \"Gas Type\", \"Option2 Value\": \"Liquid Propane\"}, {\"Variant Name\": \"ILVE - Nostalgie II Gas Cooktops - UHCP36FNSSG\", \"Variant Inventory Tracker\": \"shopify\", \"Variant Inventory Qty\": \"10\", \"Variant SKU\": \"UHCP36FNSSG\", \"Variant Image\": \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UHCP36FNSSG_p136622.jpg\", \"Variant All Images\": [\"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UHCP36FNSSG_p136622.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"3999.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202592147\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \"      <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\">         <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"product-desc\\\"><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>ILVE 36\\u2033 Built-In Gas Cooktop with 4\\u00a0Burners and Griddle, in Stainless Steel</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">The taste of tradition, with a modern twist.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">The perfect blend of past and present, creating the very heart of your home. Nostalgie is the cooking system that combines elegant retro aesthetic inspiration with cutting edge technologies.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><ul style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><li>Dual gas burner</li><li>Sturdy cast iron pan grates</li><li>Safety valve</li><li>Total Black brass burner with non-stick nanotechnological coating</li><li>Electric ignition\\u00a0Integrated in the knobs</li><li>Continuously adjustable flame</li></ul><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Product Technologies</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Aesthetics is important, but it\\u2019s not all. It is essential to have the best technologies available to cook well and with pleasure.\\u00a0ILVE puts all its experience and research at your service, offering solutions that combine top-level\\u00a0performance\\u00a0and maximum simplicity, safety and user-friendliness: to always guarantee the best satisfaction.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Total Black Brass Burner\\u00a0with Non-Stick Nanotechnological Coating</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">The noble technical characteristics of brass are enriched with a nanotechnological coating that assures easy cleaning, with an elegant black finish.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Cooktop (Hob) with Cast Iron Pan Supports</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">The highly durable, cast-iron pan grates provide a functional and safe support for all sorts of pots and pans.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p><strong>Limited 2 Year Parts and Labor Warranty</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>California Proposition 65</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">WARNING: Cancer and Reproductive Harm</p><p><a href=\\\"http://www.P65Warnings.ca.gov\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">www.P65Warnings.ca.gov</a></p></div>.<br><br><strong>Freight Charges May Apply</strong><br><br></div>      </div>      <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_accessories\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab\\\" aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_accessories\\\" data-slug=\\\"accessories\\\" role=\\\"tab\\\" aria-selected=\\\"false\\\" tabindex=\\\"-1\\\"> <span class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtext\\\">Accessories</span> </span></h3>      <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_accessories\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_accessories\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\">         <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\">                     